data.title: Func HS-260 3.5mm Connector Circumaural Gaming Headset Overview
data.description: Enjoy amazing sound and superior comfort with the HS-260 gaming headset. Impressive 50mm audio drivers deliver clean and crisp sound, while the closed-ear cup design with changeable ear cushions gives you the ultimate in comfort -- even after extended use. The sound and volume controls are integrated onto the left ear cup, allowing you to keep your eyes focused on the screen with minimal distractions. The added features of the removable microphone and detachable cord solution ensure that you have a well-rounded, multi-functional gaming headset.

And, a simple yet powerful drag-and-drop software interface can equip each of the nine programmable buttons with custom macros. Designed by and for hardcore PC gamers, the Tournament Edition R.A.T. Gaming Mouse is a fierce weapon that puts a full arsenal of cutting-edge features at your fingertips.

data.title: ZyXEL High Performance 2GbE SPI/500Mbps VPN Firewall Overview & Demo
data.description: Designed to tackle today's needs and to grow with your business tomorrow, the ZyXEL High Performance ZyWALL Series VPN Firewalls deliver high speed, high security, and high availability remote access to branch offices, partner offices, and mobile employees. ZyXEL's new ZyWALL Series VPN Firewalls are business-grade VPN gateways purpose-built to deliver the fastest performance for multi-site VPN deployments. These high performance VPN Firewalls feature multi-core CPUs, and are fine-tuned to deliver ultra-fast performance with exceedingly high firewall and VPN throughputs. The new ZyWALL Series VPN Firewalls also feature the most advanced VPN functionality—SHA-2 encryption, VPN HA, and L2TP—for more secure, more reliable, and more mobile VPN connectivity.

data.title: Corsair Hydro Series H105 240mm Liquid CPU Cooler Overview
data.description: The Hydro Series H105 provides extreme CPU cooling performance. The 38mm thick, 240mm top-mounted high-capacity radiator is paired with high-performance SP120L fans for powerful heat dissipation you need for highly overclocked CPUs. And, PWM fan speed fan control lets you select the precise level of cooling power you need.

data.title: GIGABYTE Aivia Uranium 10 Buttons Tilt Wheel USB RF Wireless Laser Gaming Mouse Overview
data.description: Take the Aivia Uranium as your professional gaming gear. It includes a 6500dpi (switchable to 800/1600/3200 dpi) wireless gaming mouse and a GHOST Macro Station. The GHOST Macro Station is your control center built for pro-gaming tasks, and functions as dynamic status display, a hot-switchable macro system, and an instant charging dock. The Aivia Uranium is designed to deliver extraordinary power to all your game play. Its battery lasts over 50 hours for continuous gameplay, and with the included charging cable, you'll enjoy an instant battery charge without leaving your game.
